Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你长大以后…要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事？
