Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星运输船遭不明物体袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20名船员去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军紧急应对总部认为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次事件系UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即未知敌人的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件仍在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自UE发动的第一起袭击事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天使陨落之日」后14年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府至今宣称
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法探明敌人的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民的不满日益高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来了吗 菲利特 菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 又熬夜了对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两眼通红
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁扎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午开始的启动实验 通知你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然！司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个普通孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的才能让所有人都惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 高达马上就能站起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么急…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没伤着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 原来是菲利特和艾米莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…不是高达的手臂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么装在那上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看好不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到运动性太棒了 不舍得拆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要试用高达部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得事先通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 高达是司令专门委托给菲利特的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 迟到了 菲利特 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 要迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再自作主张了 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特真是 提起高达就激动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷 您请看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是明日野家族世代相传的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的战士 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在过往的大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被称作是为世界带来和平的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些战士们 过去也被叫做MOBILE SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MOBILE SUIT?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 巨大的人形兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MOBILE SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的众多名机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出自代代经营MS制造业的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明日野家族 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要制造出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的救世主 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说吗 外星人又惹事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是UE吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来历不明 不是外星人是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只要住在诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我们没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们就没怎么来过人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我们开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 老师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师怎么看昨天的事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货船疑似被UE袭击的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 是不是也该想好应对措施？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座诺拉也不是绝对安全的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特的被害妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有危险的话 会发布警告的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到现在为止从来没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE的袭击 有一定规律性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据规律解开方程式…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 答案表明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次遭袭的就是诺拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完没完！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什么 菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看你现在成绩优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦松懈马上就会落后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为去掺和军方那个什么机动战士开发计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会满脑子这些不切实际的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当初就反对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到座位上去 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被退学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 挨骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 挨骂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人说不定已经在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离上次来天文馆 有多久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我想太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉会被袭击的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座卫星上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只把那些看成是发生在遥远世界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为谁都没有被UE袭击过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我亲眼看见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故乡奥凡在UE的袭击中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个城市瞬间化作火海的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们根本杀人不眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈临死前 给我的记忆体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说 这里面有我该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面记录有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士的设计图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前家里画像上一模一样的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是提到的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画中的救世主 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那台白色战士的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一定想说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我制造机动战士去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗中 拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以菲利特造的机动战士也叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是救世主的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 城市里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那闪光是…爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UE！ 这样下去城市就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UE…他们真的来了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人确认为UE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防卫队请出战！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士是什么情况 出动如此缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外的Genoace直接前往迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号机库 德列斯小队能否出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去出口会被控制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古鲁迪克 古鲁迪克副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥防守第四到第八防区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉你不用来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.41,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)\fs30}（全员战斗配置）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.27,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)\fs30\fad(0,400)}（重复 全员战斗配置）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE的攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是外星人 该怎么打？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 艾米莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Genoace
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 想急死我这个老头子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是UE的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是什么机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们只会到处破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台搬运车上 运的是高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赶忙把它藏到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的Genoace被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 出动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达可以战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 高达还动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离实战差远了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试时站起来走了两步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样足以确认运动性了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个 拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对第一次驾驶的人来说风险太大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用Genoace出战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 这里也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去里面避难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是驾驶员 怎么可能开得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我造的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体的情况 我最了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是了解就能打赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘·德列斯 Genoace出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赶紧打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14年来从没被人击败过的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营救驾驶员 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准去！你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 抬他出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 什么都没做成…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 大家都会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人就是那样残暴 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平衡器只能边驾驶边调节了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是想让菲利特开它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特的觉悟是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不输给大兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用妈妈给我的这台高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和它们战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来启动顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我升起托架了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不想让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直看在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特有多么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特的战斗就永远不会结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量系统 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系统 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 高达好像要出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员是拉甘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁扎先生 这是我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一定要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去救出大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野 高达出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四机库防爆舱门确认开启
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们见识见识 你传说中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大家 也为你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为救世主 与高达一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一台 就这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 有什么武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用 那么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了吗 UE的机动战士型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有增援 想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 这就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 还不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特果然是个了不起的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙什么时候变得这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们胜利了 史上首次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这种程度的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会改变任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以成为反击的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在好好享受这份胜利…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才的机动战士型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来自卫星外部的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使陨落之日 又要重演…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故乡大地被未知敌人的魔爪蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这时 高达发动真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE之力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人的命运成就历史
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TVCM------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.69,0:24:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达是根据妈妈托付给我的AGE装置
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们制造出的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和明日野家族画像上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的白色救世主高达非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.87,0:24:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我给它起名为 高达